2Z — OK\n   144→- **Log**: iteration-007.log\n   145→\n   146→## Iteration 8 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n   147→\n   148→**Item**: [backend] `routes/referral.ts`: `GET /referral/code` — return current code for authenticated wallet, or 404\n   149→**Status**: Done\n   150→**Changes**:\n   151→- Added `GET /code` endpoint to `services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts`\n   152→  - Reads wallet from JWT auth context (`c.get(\"wallet\")`)\n   153→  - Calls `db.getReferralCodeByWallet(wallet)` to look up existing code\n   154→  - Returns `{ code, url }` if found (url = `https://taunt.bet/r/{code}`)\n   155→  - Returns 404 with `{ error: { code: \"NO_CODE\", message: \"...\" } }` if no code set\n   156→  - Follows same patterns as existing `POST /code` endpoint (auth check, error shape, REFERRAL_BASE_URL)\n   157→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18)\n   158→\n   159→## Iteration 8 — 2026-03-25T11:57:51Z — OK\n   160→- **Log**: iteration-008.log\n   161→\n   162→## Iteration 9 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n   163→\n   164→**Item**: [backend] `routes/referral.ts`: `POST /referral/apply` — link referee to referrer\n   165→**Status**: Done\n   166→**Changes**:\n   167→- Added `POST /apply` endpoint to `services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts`\n   168→  - Requires JWT auth (wallet from context)\n   169→  - Validates code is non-empty string\n   170→  - Looks up referral code via `db.getReferralCodeByCode(code)` — returns 404 if not found\n   171→  - Self-referral check: rejects if `codeRow.wallet === wallet` (400, SELF_REFERRAL)\n   172→  - Existing referrer check: calls `db.getReferralLinkByReferee(wallet)` — returns 409 if already linked\n   173→  - Creates link via `db.insertReferralLink(referrerWallet, wallet)`\n   174→  - Returns `{ referrer: wallet, benefit: \"10% fee rebate on all games\" }`\n   175→  - Race condition handling: catches unique constraint violation on concurrent insert → 409\n   176→  - Error shape follows spec: `{ error: { code, message, retryable? } }`\n   177→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18)\n   178→\n   179→## Iteration 9 — 2026-03-25T12:01:01Z — OK\n   180→- **Log**: iteration-009.log\n   181→\n   182→## Iteration 10 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n   183→\n   184→**Item**: [backend] `routes/referral.ts`: `GET /referral/stats` — referral summary stats endpoint\n   185→**Status**: Done\n   186→**Changes**:\n   187→- Added `GET /stats` endpoint to `services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts`\n   188→  - Requires JWT auth (wallet from context)\n   189→  - Calls `db.getReferralStats(wallet)` which returns snake_case `ReferralStats`\n   190→  - Maps to camelCase API response: `referredCount`, `activeCount`, `totalVolumeLamports`, `totalEarnedLamports`, `pendingLamports`\n   191→  - All monetary values are lamport strings (not floats)\n   192→  - Error handling: catches and logs failures, returns 500\n   193→  - Follows existing endpoint patterns (auth check, error shape, logger)\n   194→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18)\n   195→\n   196→## Iteration 10 — 2026-03-25T12:03:21Z — OK\n   197→- **Log**: iteration-010.log\n   198→\n   199→## Iteration 11 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n   200→\n   201→**Item**: [backend] `routes/referral.ts`: `GET /referral/earnings` — paginated per-game earnings log\n   202→**Status**: Done\n   203→**Changes**:\n   204→- Added `GET /earnings` endpoint to `services/backend/src/routes/referral.ts`\n   205→  - Requires JWT auth (wallet from context)\n   206→  - Query params: `page` (default 1), `limit` (default 20, max 100)\n   207→  - Validates page/limit are positive integers, returns 400 on NaN\n   208→  - Calls `db.getReferralEarnings(wallet, page, limit)` for paginated data\n   209→  - Maps snake_case DB fields to camelCase API response: `roundId`, `gameType`, `refereeWallet`, `wagerLamports`, `earnedLamports`, `createdAt`\n   210→  - All monetary values returned as lamport strings (not numbers)\n   211→  - `createdAt` as ISO-8601 string\n   212→  - Response includes `pagination: { page, totalPages }` per 