{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HJYyPVmgRqEZ5vMykm41zt","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now let me create a comprehensive report with all the findings:\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\nI've located and read all the requested files. Here's what you need to understand for building the referral card section:\n\n---\n\n## File Contents\n\n### 1. **ReferralPage.tsx** (Current Shell)\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralPage.tsx`\n\nThe referral page is a minimal scaffold with:\n- Authentication guards (requires `connected` wallet and `isAuthenticated` session)\n- A placeholder header with subtitle\n- Four `<!-- §N: card name — implemented in next iteration -->` comments marking where sections should go:\n  1. Your Referral Link card\n  2. Stats summary card\n  3. Pending balance + Claim card\n  4. Earnings history table\n\n---\n\n### 2. **index.ts** (Barrel Export)\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/index.ts`\n\nExports:\n```typescript\nexport { useReferralApply } from \"./hooks/useReferralApply\";\nexport { ReferralPage } from \"./ReferralPage\";\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. **referral-api.ts** (API Client)\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts`\n\nKey functions relevant to the first card:\n\n**`setReferralCode(token: string, code: string): Promise<ReferralCodeResponse>`**\n- POST `/referral/code`\n- Sets (or replaces) the authenticated player's referral code\n- Returns: `{ code: string, url: string }`\n\n**`getReferralCode(token: string): Promise<ReferralCodeResponse>`**\n- GET `/referral/code`\n- Gets the authenticated player's current referral code\n- Throws on 404 if no code exists yet\n- Returns: `{ code: string, url: string }`\n\n**`applyReferralCode(token: string, code: string): Promise<ApplyReferralResponse>`**\n- POST `/referral/apply`\n- Used to apply/link to a referrer's code\n- Returns: `{ referrer: string, benefit: string }`\n\n**Other relevant functions:**\n- `getReferralStats()` - gets summary (referredCount, activeCount, totalVolume, totalEarned, pending)\n- `getReferralEarnings()` - paginated earnings log\n- `requestReferralClaim()` - async claim request, returns `{ claimId, amountLamports, status }`\n- `pollClaimStatus()` - poll claim by ID\n\n---\n\n### 4. **useReferralApply Hook**\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/hooks/useReferralApply.ts`\n\nHandles the auto-apply of referral codes on authentication:\n- Reads a code from `localStorage` under key `\"referral_code\"` (stored as `JSON.stringify({ code })`\n- On auth, calls `applyReferralCode(accessToken, code)`\n- Clears storage on permanent errors (invalid code, self-referral, already linked) OR success\n- Keeps storage on transient failures (network errors) for retry on next auth\n\n---\n\n### 5. **App.tsx** (Routes)\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` (partial read, first 42 lines)\n\nKey imports:\n```typescript\nimport { useReferralApply, ReferralPage } from \"./features/referral\";\n```\n\nReferralPage is rendered inside the router (exact route TBD, not shown in the excerpt).\n\n---\n\n## Frontend Patterns Found\n\n### ProfilePage Structure\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx`\n\n**Pattern:**\n1. Guards: loading state → not-connected state → authenticated render\n2. Header section with avatar + name/info\n3. Tabbed content (active state via `useState`)\n4. Modal for avatar selection\n5. Inline editing for username with validation\n6. Icons as SVG components (EditIcon, CheckIcon, CancelIcon)\n7. CSS classes: `profile-page__header`, `profile-page__title`, `profile-page__content`, etc.\n\n### ProfileSettings Component\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileSettings.tsx`\n\n**Card Pattern (Social Connections):**\n```typescript\n<div className=\"profile-settings__section\">\n  <h3 className=\"profile-settings__section-title\">Connected Socials</h3>\n  <div className=\"profile-socials__list\">\n    <div className=\"profile-socials__item\">\n      <div className=\"profile-socials__icon\">[SVG]</div>\n      <div className=\"profile-socials__info\">\n        <div className=\"profile-socials__name\">Discord</div>\n        {connected && <div className=\"profile-socials__username\">username</div>}\n      </div>\n      <button type=\"button\" className=\"profile-socials__btn...\" onClick={handler} disabled={loading}>\n        {loading ? \"...\" : connected ? \"Disconnect\" : \"Connect\"}\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Loading state managed with `useState(false)` per action\n- Handlers wrap async calls with try/catch + set loading state\n- Button text changes to \"...\" during loading\n- BEM naming: `feature__element--modifier`\n\n### LootPage Structure\n**Path:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/LootPage.tsx`\n\n**Minimal Page Pattern:**\n```typescript\nexport function LootPage() {\n  const { myProfile, loading } = usePlayerProfile();\n  \n  if (loading) return <div className=\"loot-page__loading\">Loading...</div>;\n  if (!myProfile) return <div className=\"loot-page__connect\">Connect Wallet msg</div>;\n  \n  return (\n    <div className=\"loot-page\">\n      <div className=\"loot-page__header\">\n        <h1 className=\"loot-page__title\">Loot</h1>\n        <p className=\"loot-page__subtitle\">Open crates and claim your rewards</p>\n      </div>\n      <div className=\"loot-page__content\">\n        <ChildComponent profile={myProfile} />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Absolute File Paths for Reference\n\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralPage.tsx`\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/index.ts`\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts`\n4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/hooks/useReferralApply.ts`\n5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx`\n6. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileSettings.tsx`\n7. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/LootPage.tsx`\n8. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx`\n\n---\n\n## Key Takeaways for Building the First Card\n\n**For §1: Your Referral Link Card:**\n\n1. **Call `getReferralCode(token)`** on mount to fetch existing code\n2. **Handle three states:**\n   - Loading\n   - No code yet (show input + \"Generate\" button)\n   - Code exists (show read-only display + copy button + regenerate button)\n\n3. **For generating/replacing code:**\n   - Render an input field + button (follow ProfileSettings button pattern)\n   - On submit: call `setReferralCode(token, code)` with user's proposed code\n   - Show \"...\" during loading, disable input/button\n   - Display success/error feedback\n\n4. **BEM naming:** `referral-link-card__`, `referral-link-card__input`, `referral-link-card__btn`\n\n5. **Reuse the social-card structure** from ProfileSettings as a template (section → item → icon/info/button)"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aafbaa4f3a015703a (use SendMessage with to: 'aafbaa4f3a015703a' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 56801\ntool_uses: 17\nduration_ms: 85710</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f0103f33-7014-49be-8433-0cd0e8f702d7","uuid":"9ae88a47-a414-46f7-9bd4-79bd19dcf05e","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:17:14.464Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":